*[[AFI百年电影史百大经典电影十周年版|AFI百年电影史百大经典电影十周年版]] - 提名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/Docs/100Years/Movies_ballot_06.pdf |title=AFI's 100 Years...100 Movies (10th Anniversary Edition) Ballot |accessdate=2013-03-22 |archive-date=2014-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328082204/http://www.afi.com/Docs/100Years/Movies_ballot_06.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
